1 0 0 1 50 505 Tm (4. SDK interface layer.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 490 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 475 Tm (CANONICAL PROCESSING MODEL) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 460 Tm () Tj
