1 0 0 1 50 280 Tm (Determinism is mandatory: equivalent inputs MUST yield equivalent outputs.) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 265 Tm () Tj
1 0 0 1 50 250 Tm (COMPATIBILITY MODEL) Tj
1 0 0 1 50 235 Tm () Tj
